  "body": "Validator client gets a panic when joins before chain start and get assignment, to reproduce:\r\n\r\n1.) Start beacon node, say chain start is at `t1`\r\n2.) Start validator client before `t1`\r\n3.) Validator client wait till `t1` to start its duties\r\n4.) Validator client gets a panic right at `t1`\r\n\r\nPanic log:\r\n```\r\npanic: runtime error: invalid memory address or nil pointer dereference\r\n[signal SIGSEGV: segmentation violation code=0x1 addr=0x0 pc=0x170c6d9]\r\n\r\ngoroutine 51 [running]:\r\ngithub.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/validator/client.(*validator).RolesAt(0xc000202120, 0x0, 0xc000123650)\r\n\tvalidator/client/validator.go:260 +0x49\r\ngithub.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/validator/client.run(0x19cf220, 0xc00006e7c0, 0x19d9220, 0xc000202120)\r\n\tvalidator/client/runner.go:79 +0x608\r\ncreated by github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/validator/client.(*ValidatorService).Start\r\n\tvalidator/client/service.go:109 +0xaa5\r\n```",
